### Claude ###
# CLAUDE.md is a gitignored relative symlink to the orchestrator's
# .claude-submodules/ — never tracked in this public repo.
/CLAUDE.md
.claude/settings.local.json

### STT benchmark — generated / derived artefacts ###
# Generated audio defaults to build/generated-audio/ (already covered by
# build/ above). A fork may redirect it to a persistent path via
# -Psttbench.generatedAudioDir=… — ignore that path here if it lives in-tree.
# PUnit explore results are reproducible from the benchmark run.
/results/**
!/results/README.md
!/results/explore/
!/results/explore/README.md
# Reports land under build/reports/stt/ (already covered by build/ above) —
# ephemeral, derived output per Gradle convention, never tracked at the root.

### Secrets / API keys ###
# Never commit provider credentials.
*.env
.env
.env.*
secrets.properties
**/credentials.json
**/*-api-key*
**/*.pem
